All other heavy vehicles, including vehicles operating under a permit that do not have the detour listed, will be escorted through the work zone by traffic control, and should call UHF 13 on approach.

Vehicles travelling under a permit must not travel off the approved route listed in their permit unless an updated permit is obtained from the National Heavy Vehicle Regulator (NHVR).

Please review the Restricted Access Vehicles map to help you plan an alternative route if required.

Operators of Class 1, 2 & 3 vehicles travelling under a Permit must not travel off the approved route listed in the permit unless an updated permit is obtained from the NHVR.
